I wanted to surprise you.

435
00:19:37,080 --> 00:19:37,920
Sorry.

436
00:19:39,320 --> 00:19:41,280
-Sorry.

437
00:19:41,840 --> 00:19:42,920
Sorry?

438
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:46,320
