449
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:16,200
and then I got this huge mushroom by my knee

450
00:20:16,280 --> 00:20:17,880
not exactly but kind of, bam bam bam,

451
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:20,160
!I have to put on some cream
