454
00:20:29,080 --> 00:20:30,400
Not standard at all.

455
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:32,600
I'm saving your whole family.

456
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:35,800
I can't take this noise anymore.

457
00:20:37,120 --> 00:20:39,120
Come on, let's turn it off.
