467
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:09,680
The engine shut off.

468
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:11,880
I love you.
-I love you too.

469
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:16,760
Okay, I fixed it
but we have to try to land.

470
00:21:16,840 --> 00:21:19,280
