472
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:26,600
This is the most beautiful wedding gift I've ever received.

473
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:30,440
Okay, I have to quote you. No, I'm dying.

474
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,880
