-Of course, come prepared for the show.

479
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:43,240
I love rehearsals.

480
00:21:43,320 --> 00:21:45,160
I'm telling you, it's a wonderful gift.

481
00:21:45,480 --> 00:21:47,080
How wonderful, Pinchas? You could've been killed.

482
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:48,360
