484
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:53,840
Dad, I could kill you myself right now.

485
00:22:00,320 --> 00:22:01,520
Isn't it wonderful?

486
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:05,080
Tell me, what is this horror?

487
00:22:05,640 --> 00:22:07,520
Sorry bro, you're going alone.

488
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:13,160
